# MrGh0st Linux Repo

## Description
MrGh0st Linux Repo is a custom Linux distribution designed for security enthusiasts and penetration testers. It includes a collection of tools and scripts to facilitate penetration testing, network analysis, and system hardening. This project aims to provide a lightweight, efficient, and user-friendly experience.

## Features
- Pre-installed security tools for penetration testing and vulnerability assessment.
- Lightweight and optimized for performance.
- User-friendly interface with easy access to tools.
- Regular updates to keep tools and packages current.

## Installation
1. Download the latest release from the [releases page](https://github.com/MR-Gh0st-OffSec/MrGh0st-Linux/releases).
2. Create a bootable USB drive using a tool like Rufus or Etcher.
3. Boot from the USB drive and follow the on-screen instructions to install.

## Usage
After installation, you can access various tools through the terminal or the application menu. For more detailed usage instructions, refer to the documentation provided within the project.

